items.badge_description: Want to enjoy a day of brews, but need to keep your wits sharp? There are plenty of delicious brews under 5% for you to sip on throughout the day. That's 270 different beers with an ABV of 5% and lower.
One cannot live on dank hops alone. Tone down the bitterness and enjoy some smooth flavor. That's 125 different beers with an IBU of 20 or below. Try 5 more for Level 26!

Hell yea helles! This traditional German pale lager is typically full-bodied, mildly sweet, and light-colored, making it a perfect go to for any occasion. That's 15 different beers with the style of Lager - Helles or Bock - Maibock / Heller (Helles) / Lentebock. Try 5 more for Level 4!
